<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-51-0420 </DOCNO><TEXT>The decentralized air ventilation device combines elements for air transportand air distribution in the form of a twisted centrifugal flow. The flowproperties of the decentralized ILKA-air ventilation device are presentedin this article which also shows its possibilities of application. Thisdevice minimizes the air handling requirements in heating and ventilatingof large industrial spaces.</TEXT></DOC>